structure.unit: LICENSING OF MOTOR VEHICLES, OPERATORS, AND TRAILERS

law.catch_line: Cabinet may prescribe methods of record keeping.
law.text: Notwithstanding the provisions of this chapter, the cabinet may by regulation prescribe methods of record keeping and reporting by the county clerk to the cabinet.
law.history: Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 384, sec. 329, effective June 17, 1978. -- Created 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 133, sec. 19, effective June 19, 1976.
